					They provide habitat for a myriad of marine species and protect
					coastlines from erosion. Climate change and pollution threaten
					these delicate structures. <span class="read-more-content">
						Making conservation efforts imperative to preserve these natural
						wonders, which support diverse marine life and benefit humans by
						protecting shorelines.</span>
				</p>
